default&#xa0;
defaultHow successful will the RHI be when rolled out to households?
defaultThis 
defaultwill
default depend on the efficiency with which the RHI is administered by Ofgem. This, in turn, 
defaultwill
default depend on the complexity of the regulations Ofgem is asked to administer.
defaultDECC has taken far too long to decide its approach and has a tendency to introduce impracti
defaultcal and confusing elements that will add to the cost of administration and present barriers to uptake.  The idea of using EPC certificates as the financial basis of administering the Domestic RHI is unhelpful. EPC certificates were introduced for other rea
defaultsons and DECC should not attempt to pass off responsibility in this way to estate agents who are not knowledgeable and are not disinterested parties.
defaultWe fear that there may be more people employed by Ofgem to administer the RHI than there will be people em
defaultployed in the country to install ground source heat pumps.
